reviewText: This set includes 2 books and 1 DVD. The first book has the episodes: The Girl Who Overcame Time and The Boy Who Was Just Overcome; Seekers of the Sacred Jewel; Down the Rabbit Hole and Back Again. The second book has the episodes: Yura of the Demon Hair; Aristocratic Assassin, Sesshomaru; Tetsusaiga, The Phantom Sword; Showdown! Inuyasha vs. Sesshomaru. The DVD has only episodes one, two and three.
